{"tid":916033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不斷更新● 九西補選】低投票率下的「黃金3小時」 李卓人呼籲投票","createTime":"2018-11-25T12:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T12:05:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8064473acf7a74f49ecaa9813566693882198312","tid":916033,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T12:05:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181125/58953648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181125%2F58953648&d=KzClu49Tl%2B%2BhyQQtCFs%2FdAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0d490d50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181125%2F58953648&h=0b32f82c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181125/58953648</a><br />\n<br />\n【不斷更新● 九西補選】低投票率下的「黃金3小時」 李卓人呼籲投票<br />\n<br />\n2小時前<br />\n即時要聞<br />\n <br />\n今日九西補選投票，港人要用選票守護香港。今次補選候選人有伍廸希、曾麗文、李卓人、馮檢基、陳凱欣，而劉小麗則被裁定提名無效，無法參選。今日各區票站位置︰ <a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2018kwby/chi/p_cs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Flegco2018kwby%2Fchi%2Fp_cs.html&d=KzClu49Tl%2B%2BhyQQtCFs%2FdAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6306c7a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2018kwby/chi/p_cs.html</a> 。<br />\n<br />\n【19:33】民主黨創黨主席李柱銘，以及「佔中」發起人之一的朱耀明，近期感冒抱恙在身的前政務司司長陳方安生，同樣冒雨在街站拉票，為的同樣是香港的未來。陳方安生認為必須守住香港的核心價值，「唔想政府一言堂、唔想立法會淪為建制派嘅天下，就請投3號李卓人，保住民主派喺立法會關鍵嘅一席。」政治明星四出拉票，無名英雄的義工亦沒有躲懶，有義工在風雨中手持橫額4小時為李卓人拉票，希望守住議會關鍵一席。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2BvzFE8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2BvzFE8&d=KzClu49Tl%2B%2BhyQQtCFs%2FdAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f9b31652\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2BvzFE8</a>"}]}